> Please click here to read the full consent form.
> If you agree to participate, please click the button below to continue to experiment instructions.
> You are about to begin the practice test.
> On each trial, you will see a sentence in English and its corresponding Spanish translation.
> You will rate the accuracy of the translation on a scale from ""Not at all accurate"" to ""Very accurate.""
> If you rate the translation as ""Somewhat innaccurate"" or ""Not at all accurate,"" you will be asked to provide your own translation or a reason why the translation is inaccurate.

> Click the button below to continue to the practice session.
